      <p class="modal-intro">The start date should be a date in the not so distance future. This allows for you to continue planning and organising your project, while still raising awareness for your cause.</p>
      <p class="modal-content">Your project will not appear on our projects page until it reaches its start date. We are currently working to add extras to our project pages so people can start reading about a project before it begins. This means you will be able to generate support for your project before you even start taking any donations! This will also give your project time to finish any paper work it might have lying about the house, such as planning permissions, etc. </p>
