      <p class="modal-content">CrowdKitty is all about supporting your local community, so stating your location will help local people find you and your project. As a CrowdKitty user, you should know that when a person registers with our site their location is used to help promote projects in their local area. If you leave this valuable piece of information out, then they might not find your local project. Make sure you are as specific as possible with your location. If you have any difficulties or queries regarding this, please contact a member of our team. Simply go to out contact us page now.</p>
